Invocation Name: health tech academy quiz
des:
HealthTech Academy Quiz provides an interactive and enriching quiz experience. Featuring dynamic question sets and score tracking, it combines fun and education seamlessly.

Key Features:
1- Interactive Quizzing: Engage in dynamic quizzes with multiple-choice questions.
2- Dynamic Question Sets: Questions are fetched dynamically from an external API, ensuring a fresh experience.
3- Score Tracking: Keep track of your quiz progress and receive a final score at the end of the session.
4- Topic Selection: Choose from a variety of topics, including Medical Assistant, Patient Care Technician, and more.

Restrictions:
1- Limited Topic Selection: The skill supports a predefined set of categories.
2- No Personalization: The skill does not support user account profiles or personalized settings.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
